5','2026-03-24 01:07:35.000000','服务内容','Service Content',NULL,'service-content',NULL,1,12,'[{\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"Help Desk\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774285444184-089b187ace17a628.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"24/7 Technical Support\", \"subtitle\": \"Remote Technical Support\", \"description\": \"Your technical inquiries will be addressed by Eneroc technical experts. Requests are efficiently directed to the relevant department for comprehensive support, with all service cases meticulously recorded.\", \"subDescription\": \"We value your daily operations and are committed to preventing unnecessary downtime. Eneroc offers timely remote services, leveraging our expertise to swiftly identify and resolve issues.\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"Onsite Repair\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774285443956-fbd759731e804800.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"Field Services\", \"subtitle\": \"Preventive Maintenance\", \"description\": \"Rely on Eneroc for swift and tailored Onsite Repair services. Our skilled technicians are equipped to promptly address and resolve issues at your location. For challenging technical issues, Eneroc responds by dispatching engineers to provide on-site service.\", \"subDescription\": \"Stay ahead of issues with Eneroc’s services. Our proactive approach involves regular inspections and adjustments to keep your systems running smoothly, maximizing equipment longevity and efficiency.\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"As your trusted partner in industrial batteries and energy systems, we offer a comprehensive selection of first-hand spare parts. Our portfolio encompasses a range of battery, charger, and system components, ensuring you have access to the essential elements needed for optimal performance and longevity. Together, we stand with you, ensuring you provide enduring and stable services to your end customers.\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774285443734-bc4fd887535d4a0f.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"Technical Hotline Spart Parts\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"Our training courses are built on a foundation of extensive technical expertise, ensuring practical and effective learning experiences. Covering batteries, storage systems, repair, safety, and end-of-life recycling, these courses provide essential knowledge for our customers and service partner candidates. Tailored to empower your team, our onsite training equips employees to confidently handle basic equipment and system errors.\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774285443328-3ae558c827f38f4a.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"Training & Certification\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}]',2,NULL,NULL,1,72,NULL),(73,1,'2026-03-24 01:40:30.881959','2026-03-24 14:14:29.000000','保修说明页',NULL,NULL,'warranty',NULL,0,13,'{\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"\", \"content\": \"<p> </p><h2>Two-Year Warranty:</h2><p>The following ENEROC products carry a two-year warranty from the date of purchase by the original end-user customer: ENEROC XXX products.In addition, any ENEROC product not categorized elsewhere in this ENEROC Warranty Statement carries a two-year warranty from the date of purchase by the original end-user customer.</p><h2>One-Year Warranty:</h2><p>The following ENEROC products carry a one-year warranty from the date of purchase by the original end-user customer:XXXXXXX, XXXXX, XXXX.</p><h2>Six-Month Warranty:</h2><p>ENEROC accessories purchased directly from our online store may carry a six-month warranty from the date of purchase by the original end-user customer.</p><h2>Discontinued ENEROC Products</h2><p>If a product is discontinued, ENEROC will, at its sole discretion, replace it with a comparable product or refund the lower of the original purchase price or the current product value.</p><h2>Used ENEROC Products</h2><p>ENEROC products purchased second-hand are not covered by the warranty.</p><p>Please note: The warranty periods set forth in this ENEROC Warranty Statement may apply to other products not listed here. If a product is not listed in this ENEROC Warranty Statement, please contact ENEROC or visit https://www.enercobattery.com/support to obtain the applicable warranty period.</p><h2>General Terms</h2><p>This ENEROC limited warranty provides you (the original end-user customer) with express limited warranty rights. If you have a separate written agreement with ENEROC, you may also have additional legal rights not excluded, restricted, or suspended by this ENEROC limited warranty. Where applicable, please refer to the \\\"Country/Region Specific Terms\\\" at the end of this warranty page for more information regarding your rights.</p><p><br></p>\", \"pic1Url\": \"\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}',2,NULL,NULL,1,73,NULL),(211,1,'2026-03-24 17:53:16.899289','2026-03-24 17:53:16.000000','业务领域与应用场景标题','BUSINESS AREAS & APPLICATION SCENARIOS',NULL,'business-areas',NULL,1,1,'[{\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"\", \"content\": \"Motive Battery\", \"pic1Url\": \"\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"\", \"content\": \"Energy Storage\", \"pic1Url\": \"\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"\", \"content\": \"Construction Machinery\", \"pic1Url\": \"\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}]',2,NULL,NULL,1,211,NULL),(214,1,'2026-03-24 18:26:19.458838','2026-03-24 18:26:19.458838','首页轮播图',NULL,NULL,'home-carousel',NULL,1,11,'[{\"url\": \"https://www.enerocbattery.com/zh/\", \"title\": \"建設機械\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploa