855-f1a47363da9af6d0.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"Paesi\", \"content\": \"Trenta\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774512380824-e75ff6a8ce8e3629.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"Ordine nel 2022\", \"content\": \"Oltre 200 milioni\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774512380778-a95c5b4ac45ddf55.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}]',6,7,NULL,1,348,NULL),(372,1,'2026-03-26 17:37:47.117762','2026-03-26 17:37:47.117762','关于我们-企业文化','企业文化','我们相信Eneroc的每一位成员都能带来改变，并致力于支持并赋能他们，共同构建一个更加可持续的未来。','about-us-culture','/uploads/202603/1774512645035-fc2473ac870a218f.png',1,8,'[{\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"视觉\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774512728927-004ca5869db550e3.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"提供可持续新能源解决方案，成为全球领导者\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"使命\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774512728892-5d39e7bf6de203b5.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"引领能源革命，共创美好未来\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}, {\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"价值\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774512728851-d484315b9f020e51.png\", \"pic2Url\": \"\", \"bigTitle\": \"\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"description\": \"专注，务实创新，创造\", \"subDescription\": \"\"}]',1,7,NULL,1,349,NULL),(373,1,'2026-03-26 17:38:01.665626','2026-03-26 17:38:01.665626','关于我们-企业文化','企業文化','私たちは、エネロックのすべてのメンバーが変化をもたらすと信じており、彼らをサポートし、力を与え、共により持続可能な未来を築くために努力しています。','about-us-culture','/uploads/202603/1774512645035-fc2473ac870a218f.png',1,8,'[{\"url\": \"\", \"title\": \"ビジョン\", \"content\": \"\", \"pic1Url\": \"/uploads/202603/1774512728927-004ca5869db550e3.png\",