h3>프로젝트 특징</h3><p>중국 최초의 해상 풍력 저장 병설 프로젝트, 저장 시스템과 해상 플랫폼의 일체화 설계.</p>','/uploads/cases/case-7-thumb.jpg','/uploads/cases/case-7-banner.jpg','[\"해상 풍력\", \"해양 저장\", \"방식 시스템\"]','[2]',NULL,3345,'','2',NULL),(42,1,'2026-03-22 18:38:08.000000','2026-03-22 18:38:08.000000','Accumulo Eolico Offshore Fujian | Caso Pengcheng','Fujian eolico offshore, accumulo marino, eolico accumulo','Caso di studio Pengcheng New Energy Fujian Pingtan 400MW eolico offshore con accumulo.',7,6,6,1,'Progetto Eolico Offshore + Accumulo Fujian','<h3>Panoramica del Progetto</h3><p>Sistema di accumulo energia da 40MW/80MWh per il parco eolico offshore di 400MW a Pingtan, provincia del Fujian, che affronta i problemi di intermittenza dell\'output eolico offshore.</p><h3>Soluzione Tecnica</h3><ul><li>Piattaforma Offshore: Sistema di accumulo ad alta anticorrosione adattato ad ambiente ad alta salinità</li><li>Configurazione Accumulo: 10% di capacità relativa all\'impianto eolico</li><li>Modalità Funzione: Levigatura output, tracciamento programma, supporto attraversamento guasti</li><li>Monitoraggio Remoto: Piattaforma offshore senza personale, monitoraggio centralizzato a terra</li></ul><h3>Caratteristiche del Progetto</h3><p>Primo progetto eolico offshore della Cina con accumulo di supporto, design integrato del sistema di accumulo.</p>','/uploads/cases/case-7-thumb.jpg','/uploads/cases/case-7-banner.jpg','[\"Eolico Offshore\", \"Accumulo Marino\", \"Anticorrosione\"]','[2]',NULL,2890,'','2',NULL),(43,1,'2026-03-22 18:38:25.000000','2026-03-22 18:38:25.000000','四川水电储能 | 鹏成新能源案例','四川储能, 水电配储, 联合调峰, 水储联合','鹏成新能源四川雅砻江水电站配套50MW/100MWh储能调峰项目案例。',8,1,7,0,'四川水电站储能调峰项目','<h3>项目概况</h3><p>四川省雅砻江水电站配套50MW/100MWh储能系统，实现水电与储能的联合调峰运行。</p><h3>技术方案</h3><ul><li>联合运行：水电与储能协同控制，响应电网调峰需求</li><li>储能配置：2小时储能系统</li><li>控制策略：水储联合AGC，响应时间<10秒</li><li>运行模式：调峰填谷、紧急备用、黑启动</li></ul><h3>项目效益</h3><p>提升水电站调峰能力30%，增加调峰收益年均超过3000万元，减少机组启停次数，延长机组寿命。</p>','/uploads/cases/case-8-thumb.jpg','/uploads/cases/case-8-banner.jpg','[\"水电储能\", \"联合调峰\", \"AGC\"]','[2]',NULL,3567,'','2',NULL),(44,1,'2026-03-22 18:38:25.000000','2026-03-22 18:38:25.000000','Sichuan Hydro Storage | Pengcheng Case','Sichuan storage, hydro storage, combined peak shaving, hydro-storage','Pengcheng New Energy Sichuan Yalong River hydropower 50MW/100MWh storage peak shaving case.',8,2,7,0,'Sichuan Hydropower Storage Peak Shaving Project','<h3>Project Overview</h3><p>A 50MW/100MWh energy storage system for the Yalong River Hydropower Station in Sichuan Province, enabling combined peak shaving operation of hydropower and energy storage.</p><h3>Technical Solution</h3><ul><li>Combined Operation: Coordinated control of hydropower and storage, responding to grid peak shaving demands</li><li>Storage Configuration: 2-hour energy storage system</li><li>Control Strategy: Hydro-storage combined AGC, response time <10 seconds</li><li>Operating Modes: Peak shaving and valley filling, emergency backup, black start</li></ul><h3>Project Benefits</h3><p>Hydropower station peak shaving capacity improved by 30%, increased peak shaving revenue exceeding 30 million yuan annually, reduced unit start-stop cycles, extended unit lifetime.</p>','/uploads/cases/case-8-thumb.jpg','/uploads/cases/case-8-banner.jpg','[\"Hydro Storage\", \"Combined Peak Shaving\", \"AGC\"]','[2]',NULL,4234,'','2',NULL),(45,1,'2026-03-22 18:38:25.000000','2026-03-22 18:38:25.000000','四川省水力貯蔵 | 鵬成新能源ケース','四川省貯蔵, 水力貯蔵, 共同ピークシェービング, 水貯連合','鵬成新能源四川省雅礱江水力発電所50MW/100MWh貯蔵ピークシェービングケーススタディ。',8,3,7,0,'四川省水力発電所貯蔵ピークシェービングプロジェクト','<h3>プロジェクト概要</h3><p>四川省雅礱江水力発電所に50MW/100MWhのエネルギー貯蔵システムを配備し、水力発電と貯蔵の共同ピークシェービング運転を実現します。</p><h3>技術ソリューション</h3><ul><li>共同運転：水力発電と貯蔵の協調制御、グリッドピークシェービング需要に応答</li><li>貯蔵構成：2時間エネルギー貯蔵システム</li><li>制御戦略：水貯連合AGC、応答時間<10秒</li><li>運転モード：ピークシェービング、緊急バックアップ、ブラックスタート</li></ul><h3>プロジェクト効益</h3><p>水力発電所のピークシェービング能力が30%向上し、年間ピークシェービング収益が3000万元を超えました。</p>','/uploads/cases/case-8-thumb.jpg','/uploads/cases/case-8-banner.jpg','[\"水力貯蔵\", \"共同ピークシェービング\", \"AGC\"]','[2]',NULL,