MW/100MWh电网储能项目案例。',15,1,14,0,'美国德州电网储能项目','<h3>项目概况</h3><p>美国德克萨斯州ERCOT电力市场50MW/100MWh电网侧储能项目，参与电力市场交易和辅助服务。</p><h3>技术方案</h3><ul><li>系统容量：50MW/100MWh，2小时储能系统</li><li>运行模式：电能量交易、调频服务、容量服务</li><li>市场参与：ERCOT电力市场、调频辅助服务市场</li><li>响应速度：毫秒级功率响应</li></ul><h3>市场收益</h3><p>年收益超过800万美元，成功参与德州电力市场多种交易品种，包括日前市场、实时市场和辅助服务市场。</p>','/uploads/cases/case-15-thumb.jpg','/uploads/cases/case-15-banner.jpg','[\"美国\", \"德州储能\", \"ERCOT市场\"]','[2]',NULL,5345,'','2',NULL),(86,1,'2026-03-22 18:40:18.000000','2026-03-22 18:40:18.000000','USA Texas Storage | Pengcheng Case','USA storage, Texas storage project, ERCOT storage, North America storage market','Pengcheng New Energy USA Texas ERCOT electricity market 50MW/100MWh grid storage project case.',15,2,14,0,'USA Texas Grid Energy Storage Project','<h3>Project Overview</h3><p>A 50MW/100MWh grid-side energy storage project in the Texas ERCOT electricity market, participating in electricity market trading and ancillary services.</p><h3>Technical Solution</h3><ul><li>System Capacity: 50MW/100MWh, 2-hour energy storage system</li><li>Operating Modes: Energy trading, frequency regulation services, capacity services</li><li>Market Participation: ERCOT electricity market, frequency regulation ancillary service market</li><li>Response Speed: Millisecond-level power response</li></ul><h3>Market Returns</h3><p>Annual revenue exceeding 8 million USD, successful participation in multiple Texas electricity market trading products, including day-ahead market, real-time market, and ancillary service market.</p>','/uploads/cases/case-15-thumb.jpg','/uploads/cases/case-15-banner.jpg','[\"USA\", \"Texas Storage\", \"ERCOT Market\"]','[2]',NULL,7123,'','2',NULL),(87,1,'2026-03-22 18:40:18.000000','2026-03-22 18:40:18.000000','アメリカテキサス貯蔵 | 鵬成新能源ケース','アメリカ貯蔵, テキサス貯蔵プロジェクト, ERCOT貯蔵, 北米貯蔵市場','鵬成新能源アメリカテキサス州ERCOT電力市場50MW/100MWhグリッド貯蔵プロジェクトケーススタディ。',15,3,14,0,'アメリカ合衆国テキサス州グリッドエネルギー貯蔵プロジェクト','<h3>プロジェクト概要</h3><p>アメリカテキサス州ERCOT電力市場に50MW/100MWhのグリッド側エネルギー貯蔵プロジェクトを建設し、